data.description: Welcome home! This beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is awaiting you to make wonderful new memories here. Immediately upon entry, you will feel welcomed by the natural lighting that pours through every window. You will also notice the open layout that is designed to create a sense of freedom and connectivity. Offering ample living space and comfort, this home is large yet very cozy. Every bedroom is spacious, offering plenty of closet and storage space. The spaciousness extends beyond the bedrooms, with generous common areas such as the living room and dining room. Upstairs, the primary bedroom gives a luxurious feeling. Once you walk through the double doors, you will feel at peace knowing this space is yours. The primary bathroom features double sinks, private water closet, and a soaking tub, which is absolutely perfect for winding down and relaxing. The backyard is completely fenced, offering extra privacy. It is the perfect space to entertain family and friends.   The charming Vista Palms community is one you will definitely want to be a part of! There are wonderful amenities that include a clubhouse, indoor fitness center, resort-style pool, hot tub/jacuzzi, splash pad, playground, and a tennis court! There are also breathtaking nature trails that will really make you appreciate not only being a Floridian, but being a Floridian that resides in this particular community! If this isn't enough for you, what if I told you that lawn maintenance is included in your HOA fee? IT IS! Take more time for yourself and have less to worry about and more to enjoy. The Southshore Bay lagoon is also just minutes away! Conveniently located just minutes from I-75, call today to make this house your home!
